        "message": "Initial commit: FBM Sniper Community Edition\n\nOpen-source Facebook Marketplace sniper with local Electron dashboard.\nFree edition: max 3 active targets, 3-minute minimum scan interval,\nrules-based scoring only (no AI grading). Data format matches Pro\nso users can upgrade without losing their watchlist or history.\n\nCo-Authored-By: Claude Opus 4.6 <noreply@anthropic.com>",
